precis:
Amendment to the LETTER MAIL REGULATIONS increasing the rates of postage
for all categories of mail included in these Regulations, including a
$0.02 increase to $0.42 (5.0 %) in the basic letter rate and standard
business letters up to 30 g, effective January 1, 1992.
